00:02.920 --> 00:04.581
NA THAN:
Previously on Heroes.

00:05.506 --> 00:07.622
You stuck your nose
where it didn't belong!

00:09.427 --> 00:10.712
HIRO: You stole something
from me.

00:10.803 --> 00:11.918
You mean this?

00:12.013 --> 00:13.093
Why are you doing this?

00:13.181 --> 00:15.672
| work for a guy.
I find stuff, he pays rne.

00:16.350 --> 00:17.931
Where's Kaito's part
of the formula?

00:18.019 --> 00:19.350
The formula is gone.
Stolen.

00:19.437 --> 00:21.018
Someone is manipulating us.

00:21.105 --> 00:22.094
Someone powerful.

00:22.190 --> 00:23.305
And they must be stopped.

00:23.399 --> 00:25.185
I will find them
and stop them.

00:25.276 --> 00:26.937
Actually,
you're the only
one who can.

00:27.820 --> 00:31.358
Cheerleader sleepover retreat?
What was that all about?

00:31.449 --> 00:33.110
That was about
buying some time.

00:33.826 --> 00:35.032
ANGELA: Meet your new partner.

00:35.119 --> 00:36.234
Am I being replaced?

00:36.329 --> 00:39.617
Just until
I find his weakness.
And then I'm gonna kill him.

00:40.124 --> 00:43.457
l've dreamt the future,
Gabriel. I've seen
how important you are.

00:43.544 --> 00:46.786
But only if you can
master your urges.

00:47.548 --> 00:49.539
My ability is not
just understanding
how things work.

00:49.634 --> 00:50.714
There's a hunger.

00:50.801 --> 00:52.928
I couldn't control it
and it turned me
into a killer.

00:53.012 --> 00:54.297
You have it now.

00:55.056 --> 00:56.091
What did you do to me?

00:56.182 --> 00:57.638
DNA manipulation.

00:57.725 --> 00:59.556
TRACY: I’ve hurt people.

00:59.644 --> 01:01.930
You need
to take it away.
I can't.

01:03.231 --> 01:06.473
You're just gonna
have to trust me, Nathan.
You must help her.

01:15.701 --> 01:18.113
NA THAN: It’s all happening
so fast.

01:18.204 --> 01:22.573
My life is a speeding train,
and I’m not sure
where it’s headed.

01:22.667 --> 01:26.785
But one thing is certain.
/ have been given a second
chance, touched by God,

01:26.879 --> 01:30.497
and l have got to
believe that he has
a purpose for my life.

01:33.135 --> 01:35.342
So why am / filled
with self-doubt?

01:36.347 --> 01:41.341
Plagued by demons,
real and imaginary.

01:43.521 --> 01:48.811
Frightened by the challenges
ahead, and haunted
by the ghosts of my past.

01:51.195 --> 01:53.311
Does God know
what / am?

01:54.407 --> 01:55.692
Do I?

01:57.535 --> 02:04.156
Am / an angel or a monster?
A hero or a villain?

02:05.751 --> 02:07.537
And why can’t/
see the difference?

02:13.884 --> 02:15.545
