because you're not
really here, are you?

02:23.728 --> 02:25.810
Whatever makes
you happy, Nathan.

02:25.896 --> 02:29.730
You know what
would make me happy?
Some straight answers.

02:30.526 --> 02:32.391
Like how you knew
she was in trouble.

02:32.486 --> 02:33.692
You mean Tracy?

02:35.364 --> 02:37.901
You said she needed my help.
That she was my path.

02:38.784 --> 02:41.275
Next thing I know,
she's taking a header
into the Potomac.

02:41.370 --> 02:45.830
And you were there to
save her. Now, I suppose
you're wondering why.

02:45.916 --> 02:49.408
I mean, was it luck?
Was it coincidence?

02:49.545 --> 02:52.912
Or perhaps guidance
from a higher power?

02:59.430 --> 03:02.342
You're not a messenger
from God.

03:02.433 --> 03:07.598
Moses saw a burning bush.
Mary heard the angel.

03:09.065 --> 03:11.932
God came to Samuel
in his dreams.

03:12.818 --> 03:16.436
And I've got a dead
mobster telling me
he's the voice of God.

03:17.281 --> 03:22.150
You think the answers to
your questions are somehow
outside of you, Nathan,

03:22.286 --> 03:25.403
but God resides within.

03:26.123 --> 03:27.533
The answers will come.

03:27.625 --> 03:28.956
TRACY: Nathan?

03:31.837 --> 03:33.293
Who are you talking to?

03:35.800 --> 03:38.837
Nobody.
Just clearing my head.

03:41.472 --> 03:43.633
