04:58.966 --> 05:00.251
Are you okay?

05:02.595 --> 05:04.335
Is he gonna be all right?

05:04.430 --> 05:07.046
Yes.
I'll make sure of it.

05:25.034 --> 05:26.899
We got a lead
on a new target.

05:28.120 --> 05:29.906
You want me
to come with you?

05:31.790 --> 05:34.122
Don't make this harder
than it already is.

05:41.967 --> 05:43.298
God. Oh, God.

05:44.428 --> 05:46.419
Sandra?
Crap!

05:48.599 --> 05:49.679
What's going on?
Claire lied.

05:49.767 --> 05:52.224
There was no cheerleader
retreat. Now she's
not answering her cell.

05:52.311 --> 05:56.179
I'm so dang stupid.
She's obviously gone
after one of them.

05:56.273 --> 05:59.015
That's all she's been
talking about.
Wanting to help.

05:59.109 --> 06:00.849
No thanks to you.
Okay, calm down.

06:00.945 --> 06:03.277
