Look at them,
they're monsters.

06:03.364 --> 06:04.945
Claire can't
get hurt, remember?

06:05.032 --> 06:06.021
Oh, no?

06:06.951 --> 06:09.363
How about this guy?
Stephen Canfield.

06:09.453 --> 06:12.365
He creates vortexes,
makes people disappear.

06:12.456 --> 06:14.617
Forever. Even Claire.

06:16.961 --> 06:18.792
All right,
we'll find her.

06:19.421 --> 06:20.410
(SIGHING)

06:27.596 --> 06:28.711
