in the middle of the night.

11:56.425 --> 11:58.165
I didn't even get
to say goodbye.

11:58.677 --> 12:01.419
They put me away for almost
two years. My family must
think I abandoned them.

12:01.513 --> 12:03.674
That's what happens
to people like you.

12:03.765 --> 12:06.256
They put you away
so the rest of us
can be safe.

12:07.936 --> 12:09.676
I made one mistake.

12:12.190 --> 12:14.055
But you're like
the others.

12:14.151 --> 12:16.062
So quick to judge,
you want to believe
I'm a monster.

12:16.153 --> 12:19.737
You killed someone.
You are a monster.

12:19.823 --> 12:22.860
