You know about me?

14:47.637 --> 14:50.424
| read your file.
You killed a man.

14:50.515 --> 14:51.800
That was an accident.

14:53.185 --> 14:57.645
Your neighbor, right?
Over what?
A broken lawn mower?

15:01.151 --> 15:02.732
We got into an argument.

15:04.404 --> 15:08.397
