I reached out
to grab him,

17:11.740 --> 17:14.527
froze him.
He shattered.

17:15.243 --> 17:17.325
It was an accident,
Tracy.

17:17.412 --> 17:19.027
I need to turn myself in.

17:21.458 --> 17:24.996
That's probably not
a good idea. What are you
gonna tell them, Tracy?

17:30.217 --> 17:32.549
I can fly,
but I can't
talk about it.

17:32.636 --> 17:34.046
Well,
then I'll show them.

17:34.137 --> 17:35.638
You can't do that.

17:36.723 --> 17:40.932
Listen, I've been there.
I understand, I...

17:41.019 --> 17:43.635
I wanted to tell the world,
I even called
a press conference.

17:43.730 --> 17:45.231
What happened?

17:45.815 --> 17:47.225
lgotshot

17:47.984 --> 17:49.269
I died.

17:50.070 --> 17:51.901
And then I saw God.

17:52.614 --> 17:56.948
And I truly believe with
all my heart that he's got
a higher purpose for us.

17:57.744 --> 18:00.702
You think
God gave us
these powers?

18:00.789 --> 18:02.154
If he didn't,
Who did?

18:04.876 --> 18:07.618
A doctor in Reseda,
California.

18:16.846 --> 18:19.588
This is the last number
the Company has for them.

18:19.683 --> 18:22.345
It's the same area code
so they can't have gone far.

18:24.062 --> 18:26.895
Thanks, Claire.
For everything.

18:31.945 --> 18:35.278
Hi, baby. It's me.

18:36.408 --> 18:38.444
Wait, don't hang up.
Look.

18:38.535 --> 18:43.825
I know you're scared
but I love you. I need
to see you and the kids.

18:46.459 --> 18:50.122
Well, then meet me, anywhere.
The Griffith Park carousel.

